Premiere: September 16th,  2005

Director: Uwe Flade
DoP: Kristian Leschner

Single: Benzin
From the album: Rosenrot

The video for BENZIN, the first single of the album ROSENROT, was directed by Uwe Flade (Depeche Mode, Franz Ferdinand) and was shot in Berlin.
